snippet.textDisplay:
I wish more such songs were made where the original folk song is given the foreground with the Western stuff in the background. Indian city musicians seem overawed with blues etc and try to force fit it into everything destroying the original flavour. I've found very few Coke India songs that are able to avoid this. This is one of those fortunate songs.

Amazing Sarangi playing by Ut Dilshad Khan!! 🙏🙏🙏
